    "scenario": "Briefing shows: destination forecast 2,500 BKN with 5SM in light rain near your ETA; scattered convective build-ups inland. Legal VFR could still be possible. Your passenger has a nonrefundable hotel and keeps reminding you. You’re legal, but your gut says it’s tight.",
    "question": "How do you apply personal minimums to make a decision?",
