    "question": "What’s your TFR risk here, and what’s your process to avoid it?",
    "correctAnswer": "Stadium TFRs can activate around major sporting events and can easily trap “local” pilots who skip a briefing. My process: check NOTAMs/TFRs every flight (even local), use FAA-approved sources/EFB TFR overlays, and if there’s any doubt, re-route well clear or don’t go. I never assume “local = safe.”",
